    <item>
      <title>印度超越香港成为全球第四大股市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/india-overtakes-hong-kong-as-world-s-fourth-largest-stock-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度股市首次超越香港股市，这是这个南亚国家的又一壮举，该国的增长前景和政策改革使其成为投资者的宠儿。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/india-overtakes-hong-kong-as-world-s-fourth-largest-stock-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 01:28:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Motley Fool 的 McFaddin 谈市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-01-23/motley-fool-s-mcfaddin-on-markets-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Motley Fool 资产管理投资分析师 Shelby McFaddin 讨论了她最新的市场前景和投资策略。她在“澳大利亚黎明”节目中与保罗·艾伦和安娜贝尔·德鲁勒斯进行了交谈。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-01-23/motley-fool-s-mcfaddin-on-markets-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 01:25:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高盛哈祖斯谈全球经济</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-01-23/goldman-s-hatzius-on-global-economy-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛首席经济学家兼全球投资研究主管 Jan Hatzius 讨论了他对全球经济的展望。他在“Daybreak Asia”节目的“高盛亚太区全球宏观会议”间隙与伊冯·文（Yvonne Man）进行了交谈。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-01-23/goldman-s-hatzius-on-global-economy-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 01:24:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>对冲基金 Asia Genesis 因在中国问题上犯下“重大错误”而关闭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/hedge-fund-asia-genesis-shuts-after-big-mistake-on-china-trade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新加坡对冲基金亚洲创世纪资产管理私人有限公司(Asia Genesis Asset Management Pte)在中国股市暴跌和日本股市上涨后遭受“前所未有的缩水”后，即将关闭其宏观基金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/hedge-fund-asia-genesis-shuts-after-big-mistake-on-china-trade</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 00:56:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国和英国对胡塞武装发动新的打击，油价保持上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-january-23</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国和英国对伊朗支持的也门胡塞叛乱分子进行新一轮打击后，油价保持上涨，加剧了中东紧张局势，抵消了对全球供应仍然充足的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-january-23</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 00:12:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国考虑新的救助方案，亚洲股市上涨：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-22/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于政策制定者正在考虑采取新的救援措施以稳定低迷市场的消息，中国股市上涨，亚洲股市上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-22/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 22:35:03 GMT</pubDate>
